description: Curbie's Sidewalk Cafe in Orlando has all your favorites! Ever have a Hot Dog from Chicago, New York or Seattle? How about Spaghetti served Cincinnati style in a Bread Bowl? A Green Chili Cheeseburger from the Southwest? California Fish Taco? Jumbalaya in a wrap? Now you can! We are serving America's Regional Favorites in locations all over Central Florida.We buy most of our food locally: Produce from Farmers Markets and Baggs Produce, Meat products are purchased from Hopkins Meat. Our Black Angus Beef has a born on date so we know it's fresh. Always striving to make it "Local, Fresh, Delicious!"
name: Curbie's Sidewalk Cafe
